Parses scopes and filters in something akin to JSON style

For instance, scope list ["users", "groups!group=foo", "servers!server=user/bar", "servers!server=user/baz"]
would lead to scope model
{
   "users":scope.ALL,
   "admin:users":{
      "user":[
         "alice"
      ]
   },
   "servers":{
      "server":[
         "user/bar",
         "user/baz"
      ]
   }
}
